-- Romanian Banca Transilvania H1 net profit up
-- 
-- Mon Aug 04, 2014 03:21AM EDT
-- None



BUCHAREST, Aug 4 (Reuters) - Romanian lender Banca Transilvania <ROTLV.BX> net profit rose by 17.7 percent on the year to 212.1 million lei ($64.28 million) in the first half, in line with expectations.

Analysts at Raiffeisen had forecast Banca Transilvania's first-half net profit at 214.3 million lei against a profit of 180.2 million lei in the first half of 2013.